      "title": "Limited bus services during the weekend",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Lanka Private Bus Owners' Association says that limited buses will be in service during the week, citing the shortage of fuel.",
        "In the meantime, Sri Lanka Transport Board (SLTB) said that buses will operate today (27) as usual.",
        "Further, Sri Lanka Railways also said that trains will operate today (27) as usual."
      ],
